{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qifeng-009__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qifeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-qifeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·齊風·009.1", "text_original": "敝笱在梁，其魚魴鰥。齊子歸止，其從如雲。", "text_normalized": "敝笱在梁，其魚魴鰥。齊子歸止，其從如雲。", "notes": "敝笱 Chinese stanza 1."}
